<pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 05:06:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/some-companies-change-tack-china-with-no-recovery-sight-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>上海警方出动警力制止喧闹的万圣节庆祝活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/police-out-force-prevent-rowdy-halloween-celebrations-shanghai-2024-10-28/</link><description>周末，上海警方在市中心街道巡逻，打击这座中国最国际化城市的万圣节庆祝活动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 03:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/police-out-force-prevent-rowdy-halloween-celebrations-shanghai-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>投资者等待美国经济数据 金价小幅走低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-slips-dollar-firms-market-eyes-crucial-us-data-2024-10-28/</link><description>周一金价小幅走软，受到美元和国债收益率走强的拖累，而交易员正在等待一系列美国经济数据以指导美联储的利率立场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 02:59:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-slips-dollar-firms-market-eyes-crucial-us-data-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国的私人辅导公司在镇压后走出阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-private-tutoring-firms-emerge-shadows-after-crackdown-2024-10-28/</link><description>目前还没有正式承认政策的变化。但现在政策制定者已经默许辅导行业的发展，北京方面的重点是支持创造就业机会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 02:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-private-tutoring-firms-emerge-shadows-after-crackdown-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国在年底贷款到期前推出新的贷款工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-activates-open-market-outright-reverse-repo-operations-2024-10-28/</link><description>中国央行周一推出新的贷款工具，在年底数万亿元贷款到期之前向市场注入更多流动性，支持银行体系信贷流动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 00:31:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-activates-open-market-outright-reverse-repo-operations-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>据《华盛顿邮报》报道，中国黑客从未透露姓名的特朗普竞选顾问那里收集了音频</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/chinese-hackers-collected-audio-unnamed-trump-campaign-adviser-washington-post-2024-10-27/</link><description>据《华盛顿邮报》周日报道，中国政府相关黑客截获了美国政治人物的电话音频，其中包括共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普的一位未透露姓名的竞选顾问。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/chinese-hackers-collected-audio-unnamed-trump-campaign-adviser-washington-post-2024-10-27/</guid></item><item><title>北京猛烈抨击美国军火交易后，台湾报告中国“战斗巡逻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-countermeasures-after-2-bln-us-arms-sale-taiwan-2024-10-27/</link><description>美国批准了一项可能为台湾提供 20 亿美元的一揽子计划，其中包括向台湾提供在乌克兰经过实战考验的先进防空导弹系统。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 00:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-countermeasures-after-2-bln-us-arms-sale-taiwan-2024-10-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国领导的亚投行行长批评发达国家贸易壁垒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-led-aiib-head-criticizes-advanced-nations-trade-barriers-2024-10-26/</link><description>亚洲基础设施投资银行（亚投行）行长金立群周六批评发达经济体设置贸易壁垒，包括可再生能源产品，称全球经济“不再自由贸易”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 15:36:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-led-aiib-head-criticizes-advanced-nations-trade-barriers-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，在华为处理器上发现芯片后，台积电暂停向中国公司发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-suspended-shipments-china-firm-after-chip-found-huawei-processor-sources-2024-10-26/</link><description>华为被限制购买该技术以保护美国国家安全。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 15:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-suspended-shipments-china-firm-after-chip-found-huawei-processor-sources-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国在美国会议上表达对关税和制裁的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-expresses-concern-over-tariffs-sanctions-us-meeting-2024-10-26/</link><description>中国财政部周六表示，中国在华盛顿举行的两国经济工作组会议上表达了对美国关税和与俄罗斯相关制裁的担忧。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 08:16:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-expresses-concern-over-tariffs-sanctions-us-meeting-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴支付 4.335 亿美元和解股东垄断诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-pay-4335-million-settle-shareholder-lawsuit-over-monopoly-claims-2024-10-26/</link><description>中国阿里巴巴周五表示，已同意支付 4.335 亿美元，以和解投资者在美国提起的集体诉讼，指控这家电子商务巨头存在垄断行为。</description><pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 03:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-pay-4335-million-settle-shareholder-lawsuit-over-monopoly-claims-2024-10-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国黑客针对与哈里斯竞选活动有关的手机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-targeted-phones-used-by-trump-vance-new-york-times-reports-2024-10-25/</link><description>一位知情人士周五表示，侵入 Verizon 系统的中国黑客瞄准了与民主党总统候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 竞选活动有关联的人员使用的手机。</description><pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 18:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-targeted-phones-used-by-trump-vance-new-york-times-reports-2024-10-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>